{"tid":2424051,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國在南海 美濟礁 衛星照曝光  大興土木全面升級成軍事基地！","createTime":"2021-02-26T09:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T13:53:42.000Z","uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aa38cba9c1e9426d8da479aba14e34a24f6d92f1","tid":2424051,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"美國持續派軍艦到南海執行「航行自由」任務，挑戰中國的主權聲索之際，多家西方媒體引述一間科技公司的南海局勢報告，指根據衛星照片，中國在有主權爭議的美濟礁上，擬修建軍事設施，擬將全面升級成軍事基地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導指，美國科技公司Simularity於2月16日公佈據衛星照片分析的「南海快速警報報告」顯示，距離菲律賓巴拉望島約100多海里、由中國控制的美濟礁的7個地點，由2020年5月7日到2021年2月4日間發生明顯變化。<br />\n<br />\n其中包括一個在去年12月初，開始建造的圓形建築基礎，而在去年5月那裡還是一片空地；島礁上另外一處修建了新的雷達罩；還有一個地方在去年10至11月出現了新的建築結構；而今年的衛星圖片還顯示，美濟礁上一些地點的建築結構被拆除。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓大學海洋事務與海洋法研究所所長Jay Batongbacal在CNN最近的報導中說，早在去年10月中國就在美濟礁建好了新的雷達設施。他認為，新設施表明中國有「長期打算」。<br />\n<br />\nBatongbacal向菲律賓媒體說：「他們（中國人）正增設觀察設備，顯然是雷達，在島礁上已經有很多雷達。」他還說，增設新雷達說明中國在加強人工島的功能，表明中國真正的意圖是把這些人工島變成「全面的軍事基地」。<br />\n<br />\n《菲律賓星報》曾在2016年1月報導，中國在美濟礁建設潛艇停靠港。<br />\n<br />\n美濟礁現時是南沙群島中面積最大的島嶼，位處中國控制島嶼的最前沿，被稱為中國的「海上前哨」，長期成為南海爭議的焦點。菲律賓及越南均聲稱擁有美濟礁的主權。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"93a8d677d96765b4583647abbd71298b5ba4fd98","tid":2424051,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/qMUt-ufgoYRa3OmVE9Y5t1SCync=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2WJR52PPRZGD3FHGDQZLUNA6WU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqMUt-ufgoYRa3OmVE9Y5t1SCync%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2WJR52PPRZGD3FHGDQZLUNA6WU.jpg&h=4dbf85a8&s={SIZE}\" />對比衛星照片後，顯示島上新建了圓形建築，疑是雷達設施。翻攝網路"},{"pid":"395d1d85ea404e0135aa42c41c1baf1d661b72b3","tid":2424051,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"開戰未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ea28a8a15876ff22b12b3ada07b27d8da060b9","tid":2424051,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/NYfKL9GatT4iFJoBJiMMmWw520E=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZBKN3W4WDNHLXHCQIZWI6EWKTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNYfKL9GatT4iFJoBJiMMmWw520E%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZBKN3W4WDNHLXHCQIZWI6EWKTA.jpg&h=82ecf05f&s={SIZE}\" />美濟礁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/BYoWwfQsGLWC7G0ANzQYXR8VUhQ=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4GIV32YPL5D73KHRVCGWAUZGD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBYoWwfQsGLWC7G0ANzQYXR8VUhQ%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4GIV32YPL5D73KHRVCGWAUZGD4.jpg&h=c306d9a8&s={SIZE}\" />美國科技公司從衛星照片分析發現，中國在美濟礁大規模修建建築設施，擬將其變成軍事基地。翻攝網路"},{"pid":"41ab84b872a3c9c76699b1917153e311912e4261","tid":2424051,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:40:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210226/LRW35OUNEFEBRPDH4R6QIKY6ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210226%2FLRW35OUNEFEBRPDH4R6QIKY6ZU%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=cbe6dd5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210226%2FLRW35OUNEFEBRPDH4R6QIKY6ZU%2F&h=55daed4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210226/LRW35OUNEFEBRPDH4R6QIKY6ZU/</a>"},{"pid":"dd68d08d00748ab77dcdd73a8668bdcba97d41c0","ti